column2: It is time to correct the injustice served on a victim of spousal abuse.  Many of us were fooled by Amber Heard's lies.  We are all embarrassed and ashamed now, however, we CAN and MUST correct this injustice.....worldwide!  Courts have made mistakes and courts have also had the courage to rectify those mistakes, especially when new evidence substantially vindicates the wrongly convicted.  It is our duty as a democratic system, to reverse a decision we later find to be made in unintentional error.  Admit the mistake and overturn the UK case.

column2:
Johnny Depp is one of the most respected, beloved actors in the world. This is what it took to tear him down to the ground: 
1. The perjury of one PROVEN abuser & liar.
2. A story in a tabloid you wouldn’t use to line a cat box.
3. One corrupt and/or compromised judge. 
Terrifying and shameful, this is spitting in the face of true victims of violence. There are MILLIONS of us worldwide fighting for justice. Amber Heard belongs in prison. Johnny Depp deserves SO MUCH better than this from Warner Bros and Disney. You should be ashamed.
